import { Container, Divider, FormControlLabel, FormGroup, List, ListItem, ListItemText, Stack, Switch, TextField } from '@mui/material';
import React from 'react';



function App() {
  return (
    <div>
      <Container maxWidth="sm">
      <List>
      <ListItem button>
        <ListItemText primary="Dados de cadastro dos peixes" />
      </ListItem>
      <Divider />
      </List>
      <Stack spacing={2} direction='row' justifyContent="center"  >
        <Stack direction='column' spacing={2} alignItems='center'  >

          <TextField

            label="PitTag"
            variant='outlined'
            color='primary'
            required

          />

          <TextField

            label="Comprimento Padrão"
            variant='outlined'
            color='primary'
            required
          />


          <TextField

            label="Local de Captura"
            variant='outlined'
            color='primary'
            required
          />
          <TextField

            label="Data de Soltura"
            variant='outlined'
            color='primary'
            required />
          <TextField

            label="Código da Amostra de DNA"
            variant='outlined'
            color='primary'
            required />
        </Stack>

        <Stack direction='column' spacing={2} alignItems='center'  >

          <TextField

            label="Nome Científico da Espécie"
            variant='outlined'
            color='primary'
            required

          />
          <TextField

            label="Comprimento total"
            variant='outlined'
            color='primary'
            required

          />
          <TextField

            label="Peso na Soltura"
            variant='outlined'
            color='primary'
            required

          />
          <TextField

            label="Local da soltura"
            variant='outlined'
            color='primary'
            required

          />
        <FormGroup>
      <FormControlLabel label="Recaptura" control={<Switch defaultChecked />}  />
      
    </FormGroup>
        </Stack>
      </Stack>

      </Container>
    </div >

  );
}

export default App;
